msgid "Move Malin and Darken Volk into the Mage Lord’s manor"
msgstr "马林和达肯·佛克进入法师领主的庄园"

#. [message]: speaker=Darken Volk
#: data/campaigns/Descent_Into_Darkness/scenarios/07_A_Small_Favor.cfg:311
msgid ""
"The stolen book lies within Lord Karres’s manor on the north end of the "
"city. We cannot defeat the entire city guard, so we must stay hidden as long "
"as possible. The cover of the night and this fog will aid us. Once we are "
"seen by the night watchmen, we will have to make a run for it. Our forces "
"are not strong enough to take the whole city."
msgstr ""
"被盗的书在城市最北面的卡瑞斯领主庄园里。我们没法打倒所有的城市守卫，所有我们"
"必须尽可能久地潜伏着。夜幕和雾气会掩护我们的。一旦被守夜人发现，我们只能逃"
"跑。我们的部队还没强大到可以征服整个城市。"

#. [message]: speaker=narrator
#: data/campaigns/Descent_Into_Darkness/scenarios/07_A_Small_Favor.cfg:316
msgid ""
"Note: Only the units you recruit now will be available to you once inside."
msgstr "注意：只有你在此时征募的部队才能在庄园的内部战斗。"

#. [message]: speaker=unit
#: data/campaigns/Descent_Into_Darkness/scenarios/07_A_Small_Favor.cfg:334
msgid ""
"Sir! Undead creatures are coming out of the forest! Wake the guard "
"immediately!"
msgstr "长官！亡灵生物从森林里出来了！立刻叫醒守卫！"

#. [message]: speaker=Taylor
#: data/campaigns/Descent_Into_Darkness/scenarios/07_A_Small_Favor.cfg:339
msgid "To arms, men!"
msgstr "大家拿起武器！"

#. [message]: speaker=unit
#: data/campaigns/Descent_Into_Darkness/scenarios/07_A_Small_Favor.cfg:358
msgid "Ooouuuh! It burns... burrrrnnns..."
msgstr "哦呜啊啊啊啊啊！烧起来了……烧起来了！！！"

#. [message]: speaker=Malin Keshar
#: data/campaigns/Descent_Into_Darkness/scenarios/07_A_Small_Favor.cfg:380
msgid "What in the name of all demons of hell was this thing?"
msgstr "以地狱中所有恶魔的名义，那到底是什么鬼东西？"

#. [message]: speaker=Darken Volk
#: data/campaigns/Descent_Into_Darkness/scenarios/07_A_Small_Favor.cfg:385
msgid ""
"This was the impact of what is known as holy water among common people. It "
"is brewed in a complicated and mysterious procedure only known to a few "
"priests and often used to fight resurrected creatures."
msgstr ""
"这就是被通常的人们称为圣水的东西的影响。它的酿造是个神秘而复杂的，只有少数牧"
"师知晓的过程。圣水常被用来对付还魂的生物。"

#. [message]: speaker=unit
#: data/campaigns/Descent_Into_Darkness/scenarios/07_A_Small_Favor.cfg:413
msgid "Here is the entrance! Hurry!"
msgstr "入口在这里！快！"

#. [scenario]: id=08_A_Small_Favor2
